snippet.title: Seiken Densetsu 3 Trailer
snippet.description: This is a trailer I made for Squaresoft's Seiken Densetsu 3 for the SNES. It displays various events, areas, music, and battles. For some reason YouTube's Flash codec encoded some of this movie's music without certain beats. If you want to download a high quality version of this movie (especially with proper music) or download the game, you can do so at my shrine for it at http://fantasyanime.com
